{"tid":940180,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"林峯大方認與張馨月甜遊東京 吳千語復合無望","createTime":"2018-12-13T17:14:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-13T17:25:10.000Z","uid":186431,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d8211d5846e9d4be8d60050f70b65b54dd66ad13","tid":940180,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T17:14:36.000Z","msg":"【#娛樂Gossip - 前事最怕有人提起！林峯大方認與張馨月甜遊東京 吳千語復合無望】<br />\n<br />\n林峯同吳千語喺幾個月前分手，不過有傳千語 BB 對林峯未斬情絲，一心想同佢復合，仲喺微博 like 咗篇關於「我錯過你了，你也錯過最好的我了」嘅戀愛千字文，真係難離難捨咁款。<br />\n<br />\n不過今次真係要放手放開所有，因為大陸34D火辣辣女模張馨月已經坐穩「新任峯女郎」呢個寶座，早前比記者影到佢同林峯東京甜蜜雙人遊，睇嚟戀情已經非常穩定。琴晚林峯出席頒獎禮，就首次大方承認同女友旅行，仲話「我嘅生活好開心」添！峯囝咁風騷，佢下年就40歲，好多人都關心佢幾時結婚，佢就話要度一度期，因為下年好忙喎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HQnD2F9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHQnD2F9.png&h=72210e50&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"935bc0c2336f885a1be380ae13daac15b0518f46","tid":940180,"uid":145194,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T17:15:46.000Z","msg":"峰仔值得更好"},{"pid":"5dc8759f2ea644edfd240235d032e083f8920178","tid":940180,"uid":38904,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T17:16:53.000Z","msg":"To 吳千語, <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/10/21/211725_828a9d7900e5692fe400c37182e2589c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F10%2F21%2F211725_828a9d7900e5692fe400c37182e2589c.jpg&h=c0aac59d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6bc30d34f1da7b448ea29ed77820092d50099a4b","tid":940180,"uid":10757,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T17:21:34.000Z","msg":"復合 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  望下人對波"},{"pid":"3e04b52b12504c03d49a07b92f4d5c1d7b9ef2d1","tid":940180,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T17:23:57.000Z","msg":"已經一齊去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/n